{"tid":32262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國西部驚現福島輻射魚　專家：對人體無害","createTime":"2016-12-10T05:49:19.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T07:09:32.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c26471475e8cde9bf3b88ac6cfaa052d4198d0d","tid":32262,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:49:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161210/640_d0e3a5c4fa6cf5ff20b0f078a2d62927.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161210%2F640_d0e3a5c4fa6cf5ff20b0f078a2d62927.jpg&h=9bc2bfe2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國研究機構「伍茲霍爾海洋研究所」(Woods Hole Oceanographic Institution)近日在奧勒岡州的提拉穆克灣(Tillamook Bay)及黃金海灘(Gold Beach)發現輻射魚，並相信這些輻射魚來自日本福島，這也是美國西部海岸首次觀測到有福島輻射魚的出沒。<br />\n<br />\n為何科學家會推斷這些魚來自福島？據《今日美國報》報導，因為這些魚都被檢測出含有「銫-134」(Cesium-134)的有毒輻謝污染物，「銫-134」也被稱作是福島核災的「指紋」。而先前也有報告指出，加拿大的鮭魚也被驗出含有「銫-134」輻射物質。<br />\n<br />\n但科學家指出，現在看到輻射魚身上的輻射毒物含量，已經非常低，對人體不會造成傷害。<br />\n<br />\n（施旖婕／綜合外電報導"},{"pid":"4c205a9b32299b8eab535a40ecc841a70a009021","tid":32262,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:51:17.000Z","msg":"41J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db11b2b81dd644ec1844b100e110ac292e092b66","tid":32262,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:53:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"532faf34ffe735ec5b2d735ad830a93e176ce2d1","tid":32262,"uid":23322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:54:37.000Z","msg":"食得之但係望到佢個咀都食唔落啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31d5bd6bd54b051a2e425a25aafe662f37104978","tid":32262,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:58:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食得之但係望到佢個咀都食唔落啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg